立法機關就名存實亡，收回立法權力，可以推行國家保護法，消滅異己，令我地依一代既反對聲音消失，中共目的達成。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家成功左一半有多 <br />\n樓上都有人講：係咁架啦  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"063f4d38b35937cc14a1231eb968834bd22a2802","tid":40004,"uid":30510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T03:48:30.000Z","msg":"人地笑係笑香港咁垃圾嘅人都做到主席<br />\n個社會戇鳩成咁人唔笑狗都吠"},{"pid":"49b3f07fc94af8a048b48c1a91de137df7e1d724","tid":40004,"uid":7985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T03:49:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係咪聽到蔣講「冇家教」 定聽錯</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無聽錯 我都聽到 真係好嬲 同你講道理無啦啦話人無家教 個腦係咪無撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ef09cd3eb80d83c293ef516eb1b1b30e28d87d5","tid":40004,"uid":328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T03:52:05.000Z","msg":"蔣麗芸議員，我建議你考慮少啲講啲冇乜用嘅說話，尤其是你個咪，好刺耳。"},{"pid":"9be508766fdb5b3b81c9375623e2e0f742561ebc","tid":40004,"uid":4324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T03:53:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我係咪聽到蔣講「冇家教」 定聽錯</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無聽錯 我都聽到 真係好嬲 同你講道理無啦啦話人無家教 個腦係咪無撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢啲唔得體既說話，佢作為主席點可以講<br />\n唔掛得曾鈺城成日唔俾面佢"},{"pid":"b8ab58fe6048856b43bd02583f15316a5486fde4","tid":40004,"uid":45285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T03:55:38.000Z","msg":"我唔知你所講既好好笑係咪開心個種？<br />\n<br />\n但我睇完都會笑，係恥笑個種笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8291d8c07f9b91cace7ad7da8da3345bf8f1c8d2","tid":40004,"uid":21222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T03:56:25.000Z","ms